<ab facs="#facs_66_r1l27"><expan>ır<ex>er</ex></expan> gute ſelber niht <expan>v<ex>er</ex>treten</expan> mügen / als das ewr gnade ſelber </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_66_r1l28">auch wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſten</expan> mag / das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir vmb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_66_line_1595313909771_48"><gap reason="illegible"/></ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan></del> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_66_r1l29">ewr gnedig <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſ<ex>chriben</ex></expan> <expan>Antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>bıte<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir 
<del rend="strikethrough"> beẏ </del> darauff wider / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_66" id="31v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Bysschoff czu <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> vormals
                            <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und den
                            <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
<expan>Swarczemb<ex>er</ex>ger</expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        diener, czu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> gesant <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von der
                        ladung wegen, als <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> pruder, Dyetrich von
                        Eglofstein, des <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Rumels und
                                <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> Paumgartners,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>, gut für <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
                        lantgerihte gen <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> geladen hat. Also hat uns
                        der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> diener,
                        wol gesagt, wie im <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan> brief an <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> pruder darümb <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        hab. Nu wöll doch derselb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> pruder davon niht
                        lassen. <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>willige<ex>n</ex></expan> dinste <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> pruder, <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> der czu
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden kume, daran weysen wollet, daz
                        er <add>noch</add> von sölcher klag und ladung, als er
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> auf der <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, gute getan hat, lasse; wölt er aber des ye
                        niht tun, daz ir doch <add>von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan></add> mit im ausztragen und bestellen
                        wöllet, daz dieselb klag und ladung <expan>aufgeschob<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        werde auf ein czeite, so die <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>uns<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>, <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ire gute
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>antwurtten</expan> und
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>treten</expan> mügen, <expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        sie czu der czeit von unfrids und sölcher fremder leuffe <add>wegen</add>,
                        als <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> in den landen sind,
                                <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> gute selber niht
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>treten</expan> mügen, als das ewr gnade selber auch
                        wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sten</expan> mag. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        wir umb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> etc. Ewr gnedig
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>s<ex>chriben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>bite<ex>n</ex></expan> wir darauff wider.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
